II. The Alpha Point: Matthew 13 as the Beginning of the Knowing-God Matrix\
\
Alpha Point: The beginning of divine wisdom in the New Covenant. Jesus\'92 teaching in parables activates the Gospel as a generative framework for spiritual understanding.\
\
Key Insight:\
	\'95	The Word is the initiator of spiritual life.\
	\'95	The hearing of the Word determines the fruitfulness of the soul.\
	\'95	This starting point (seed) must be received, understood, and cultivated for theology to be lived knowledge rather than abstract theory.\
\
III. Triadic Wisdom Structure of the Seed Parables\
\
Matthew 13 can be understood through three fractal layers:\
	1.	Physical Layer (Creation)\
	\'95	Seed: Physical propagation.\
	\'95	Soil: The heart receiving teaching.\
	\'95	Fruit: Real, visible evidence of growth.\
	2.	Covenantal Layer (The Spiritual Heart)\
	\'95	Seed: The Word of God.\
	\'95	Soil: The Covenant promises received by faith.\
	\'95	Fruit: Righteous works manifesting the life of faith.\
	3.	Eschatological Layer (The Harvest and Judgment)\
	\'95	Seed: Christ as the Word Incarnate.\
	\'95	Soil: The Global Church.\
	\'95	Fruit: The Final Judgment\'97wheat gathered, tares burned.\
\
